neral.&#10;3. The government has not shown the same level of eagerness in funding antibody testing for the coronavirus as they have in supporting the new Auditor General. While the Prime Minister has expressed fervor for dealing with the coronavirus, the transcript does not indicate that he has shown the same enthusiasm for antibody testing as he has for obtaining a vaccine. The opposition has questioned this discrepancy but has not received a clear answer from the government.">
