ese requests, instead stating that they are being transparent through daily updates.&#10;3. The government's reluctance to table an economic update may be due to the difficulty in making projections given the dynamic nature of the pandemic. They believe that their approach of providing daily information on their investments and programs is appropriate and continue to be transparent about their actions.&#10;4. There may also be a delay in providing additional support to small business owners through the Canada Emergency Business Account, as well as uncertainty around whether the wage subsidy will be extended to small businesses that have been closed and are just beginning to open now.">
